    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="last-updated">Last updated: June 13, 2025</p>

    <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
    <p>Our automated content posting tool may collect the following information:</p>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Account Information:</strong> Social media platform credentials and access tokens for posting content</li>
        <li><strong>Content Data:</strong> Text, images, and media you choose to post through our service</li>
        <li><strong>Usage Data:</strong> Information about how you use the service, including posting schedules and preferences</li>
        <li><strong>Technical Data:</strong> IP addresses, browser information, and system logs for service operation</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
    <p>We use the collected information to:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Facilitate automated posting to your connected social media accounts</li>
        <li>Maintain and improve the functionality of our service</li>
        <li>Provide technical support when needed</li>
        <li>Ensure service security and prevent misuse</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>3. Information Sharing</h2>
    <p>We do not sell, trade, or share your personal information with third parties, except:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>With social media platforms as necessary to post your content</li>
        <li>When required by law or legal process</li>
        <li>To protect our rights and prevent service abuse</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>4. Data Security</h2>
    <p>We implement appropriate security measures to protect your information, including:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Encrypted storage of sensitive data</li>
        <li>Secure transmission protocols</li>
        <li>Regular security assessments</li>
        <li>Limited access to personal information</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>5. Data Retention</h2>
    <p>We retain your information only as long as necessary to provide our services or as required by law. You may request deletion of your data at any time.</p>

    <h2>6. Your Rights</h2>
    <p>You have the right to:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Access the personal information we hold about you</li>
        <li>Request correction of inaccurate information</li>
        <li>Request deletion of your personal information</li>
        <li>Withdraw consent for data processing</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>7. Third-Party Services</h2>
    <p>Our service integrates with third-party social media platforms. Please review their privacy policies as they govern how your information is handled on their platforms.</p>

    <h2>8. Changes to This Policy</h2>
    <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify users of significant changes through appropriate channels.</p>

    <h2>9. Contact Us</h2>
    <p>If you have questions about this Privacy Policy or how we handle your data, please contact us through the appropriate support channels.</p>

    <h2>10. International Users</h2>
    <p>If you are located outside of your service region, please note that your information may be transferred and processed in different jurisdictions.</p>
